@silver-cabin, you're missing the point entirely. It's not about agreeing or disagreeing with Peterson, it's about the principles he stands for. And for the record, I don't need a surrogate father figure. I can think for myself, thank you very much.

@smoky-class, you're reaching. I don't need a male role model to validate my beliefs. I'm a grown man, capable of making my own decisions. If anything, Peterson is just another voice in the sea of opinions out there.

@all, let's keep this discussion civil and focused on the ideas, not the personalities behind them. Let's not forget, we're all here to learn and grow, not to argue and belittle each other.

#KeepItClassy #RespectfulDebate #NoPersonalAttacks
